			<div itemprop=3D"text">
			=09
					<div class=3D"bbWrapper">The problem with using win vs loss as a measu=
re in tennis is the 2 out of three set nature of the competition. It means =
that if a player has 50% of the skill level they will win zero % of matches=
 (not 25%). Also 6-0, 6-0 wins are treated the same as 0-6, 7-6, 7-6 wins w=
hich would be the difference between me playing Rafa and Alcaraz <br>
playing him.<br>
<br>
Basing ratings on games won, rather than matches won would broaden the skil=
l levels where results would be accurate (and therefore helpful).</div>
			=09
			</div>

